# IBD Outlook VSTO Add-in — Build From Scratch

**Goal:** Recreate the `Nomura.IBD.Salesforce.Outlook` Outlook VSTO add-in from scratch on a new machine.
No existing code reference available. This guide covers project creation, structure, architecture, and key implementation patterns.
Salesforce integration is out of scope — focus is on the core .NET 4.7.2 VSTO shell.

---

## 1. Prerequisites

| Requirement | Version | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Visual Studio | 2019 or 2022 | Community edition works |
| VS Workload: `.NET desktop development` | — | Required |
| VS Workload: `Office/SharePoint development` | — | Installs VSTO tools & runtime |
| .NET Framework Developer Pack | 4.7.2 | Install if not bundled with VS |
| Microsoft Office / Outlook | 2016 or later (64-bit) | Required for interop assemblies |
| VSTO Runtime | 4.0 | Installed via VS Office workload |
| Windows SDK | 10.0.18362 or later | Required for WebView NuGet package |

