## 12. Build & Verify

1. Build solution — no errors expected after NuGet restore
2. Expected output in `bin\Debug\`:
   - `Nomura.IBD.Salesforce.Outlook.dll`
   - `Nomura.IBD.Salesforce.Outlook.vsto`
3. Press **F5** — Outlook launches with the add-in loaded
4. Check Task Manager → Outlook process should not crash on startup
5. Check log file: `%TEMP%\Nomura.IBD.Salesforce.Outlook\Log.txt`

